    "The second baseline is Llama-3.1-70B-Instruct as a base judge and we call it 70B.",
    "The last baseline is another specialized judge JudgeLM (Zhu et al., 2025).",
    "These baselines cover more computationally costly alternatives as well as another specialized judge.",
    "To have a fair comparison, all models are queried using vLLM with the same decoding configuration: temperature = 0.1, top p = 0.9, and top k = -1 (unrestricted sampling).",
    "All reported metrics are on test sets."
